{
  "stem": "23506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got the jewelry back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I put it in-- in a shoemaker was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He put it in the-- took off the heel, and make a nest there, and put different things in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- once I was done with this business, I went to look up my Hashomer Hatzair friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to one friend's house, and the father had a candy factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said his son is in Lithuania-- that the whole group went to Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he said, there is one girl here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And her father was sick, so she didn't go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He gave me the address of this girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to this girl house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said, look, she said, there is a meeting today, that a man came from Lithuania, and he's having this meeting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he's organizing the Jewish underground in the big cities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was Mordechai Anielewicz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But at that time I didn't know who Mordechai Anielewicz was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I wanted to go to the meeting inside, I was not allowed to go to the meeting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, I still was from Hashomer Hatzair, from a different city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had to wait.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When he came back from the meeting, I told him, look, I am here on business for my parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have done everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I want to know what the movement says we should do with with our work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said like-- and I told him we meet every-- every week or every day in Meyer Sanyolevits's house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have discussions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We do politics.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We do [? think, ?] you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And just to lift up the spirit of the other, younger-- younger members.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he told me, you know, I didn't-- Piotrkow was not on my list.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
